{"tid":907591,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"遊戲永遠玩唔到結局,我既問題定GAME既問題?","createTime":"2018-11-19T02:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T08:16:37.000Z","uid":170886,"like":33,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb82a6733f8986fe8d142945751cd7f0126758b","tid":907591,"uid":170886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:15:45.000Z","msg":"本身算係重度GAME迷,<br />\n任何平台有新遊戲出品都會留意下,但主要玩PS4,手機同電腦<br />\nPS4既近年買左好撚多,有大路野,又有小眾既GAME,但好似玩到結局既GAME只有幾隻<br />\n地平線,秘境4,女神異聞錄係少數幾隻可以玩完既GAME<br />\n其他例如call of duty, 蜘蛛人, 勇者鬥惡龍都無辦法堅持到最後<br />\n玩玩下就開始覺得唔知做咩好....久唔久就開始棄game<br />\nPC既話唯一可以堅持玩既就只有虹彩,好多STEAM GAME都無辦法玩到結局<br />\n<br />\n係咪人大左只係見到新GAME就想買,而唔係真心想玩,有無巴打絲打有同感?"},{"pid":"fc561e76da730ce5970cd571ce15275b0337b693","tid":907591,"uid":221419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:16:42.000Z","msg":"虹彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63968848fd357bfd4dcca3e0648e839c553e2ca6","tid":907591,"uid":170886,"like":0,"dislike":40,"score":-40,"quote":{"pid":"fc561e76da730ce5970cd571ce15275b0337b693","tid":907591,"uid":221419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:16:42.000Z","msg":"虹彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"虹彩六號<br />\nFps"},{"pid":"3aac0bcc6fe8ad1ee246e420f563aacc74850c8b","tid":907591,"uid":189719,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb99c7357148ea6a88b0b3a908153bc577184205","tid":907591,"uid":200247,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:24:40.000Z","msg":"我都係，steam買二三百隻game，爆左得幾隻，明明根本無時間玩但成日新既一出就買，有時頂唔順自己會退款<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e840a772f0d8f21d45f078cb2dfd7da2a6cf838d","tid":907591,"uid":200247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cb99c7357148ea6a88b0b3a908153bc577184205","tid":907591,"uid"